import axios from 'axios'; import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; function Product() { const [data, setData] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { const fetchData = async () => { const result = await axios('https://fakestoreapi.com/products/'); setData(result.data); }; fetchData(); }, []); return ( <> {data.map((item) => (
{item.title}
{item.rating.rate}
${item.price} Add to cart
))} ); } export default Product;
